---
---
<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-[#FFFBFB]">
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute -right-20 top-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[#E29595]/5 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -left-20 bottom-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[#E29595]/5 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="mb-6 inline-block text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-[#E29595]">
          Boutique de Nail Art
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-medium leading-[1.1] text-[#2D2D2D] sm:text-8xl italic tracking-tighter">
          A Arte em <br />
          <span class="text-[#E29595]">Suas Mãos</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#2D2D2D]/60 font-light">
          Redescubra o prazer de mãos e pés impecáveis. Um refúgio de sofisticação onde cada detalhe é desenhado para sua beleza e relaxamento.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="#contato" class="btn-chic px-10">
            Agendar Agora
          </a>
          <a href="#servicos" class="btn-outline-chic px-10">
            Ver Serviços
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 flex items-center gap-8 border-t border-[#2D2D2D]/5 pt-8">
          <div>
            <span class="block text-xl font-bold italic text-[#2D2D2D]">2.5k+</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#2D2D2D]/40 font-bold">Clientes Felizes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-8 w-px bg-[#2D2D2D]/10"></div>
          <div>
            <span class="block text-xl font-bold italic text-[#2D2D2D]">500+</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#2D2D2D]/40 font-bold">Cores Exclusivas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal relative">
        <div class="relative z-10 overflow-hidden rounded-[60px] rounded-tr-[200px] aspect-[4/5] shadow-2xl shadow-[#E29595]/10">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1632345031435-8727f6897d53?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" 
            alt="Nail Art Premium" 
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative frame -->
        <div class="absolute -inset-4 -z-10 rounded-[60px] rounded-tr-[200px] border border-[#E29595]/20"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
